h4. Purpose

The date tag renders the current date/time in the page.

The only attribute supported is "format" which takes a Java date format pattern, in the same way the "Grails g.formateDate tag":https://grails.org/doc/latest/ref/Tags/formatDate.html does. 

If no value is supplied, it defaults to "dd MMM yyyy".

*Example* 

The date is: @<wcm:date/>@ 

This page is Copyright @<wcm:date format="yyyy"/>@ ACME Web Corp.


